Module xorcery.junit
Package com.exoreaction.xorcery.junit

Class XorceryExtension

Object
XorceryExtension
All Implemented Interfaces:
AfterAllCallback, BeforeAllCallback, Extension, ParameterResolver, TestExecutionExceptionHandler
@TestInstance(PER_CLASS) public class XorceryExtension extends Object implements TestExecutionExceptionHandler, ParameterResolver, BeforeAllCallback, AfterAllCallback
JUnit Extension to create Xorcery instances. It is possible to specify instance id (to easily look up the instance within tests), configuration, and optionally provide a Zip archive name from src/test/resources which is unzipped into home directory data.

If an archive is provided the home directory data is not deleted after the test finishes to make subsequent tests with the same test data run faster.
